description: M.O.B.A.Network AB engages in the development of e-sports and gaming products. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2019-12-12. The firm owns and operates gaming communities to electronic sport (e-sport) fans to craft gaming strategies and sharing ideas with other passionate players. The Company’s communities consist of Mobafire.com (League of Legends) and Dotafire.com (DOTA2), Smitefire.com, Heroesfire.com, Vaingloryfire.com, Owfire.com, Leaguespy.gg & Counterstats.net, and Artifactfire.com.
naics: Computer Systems Design and Related Services
